sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Sim as IoT szimulátor<br/>(setInterval, 30s)
    participant DB as SQLite<br/>shopping_centers
    participant Hist as SQLite<br/>occupancy_history
    participant FE as Frontend<br/>(DashboardPage)
    participant Q as TanStack Query<br/>(useShoppingCenters)
    participant API as Express<br/>GET /api/shopping-centers

    loop Minden 30 másodpercben
        Sim->>DB: SELECT id, capacity, occupied FROM shopping_centers
        DB-->>Sim: [{id, capacity, occupied}, ...]
        loop Minden központra
            Sim->>Sim: delta = ⌊(rand-0.5)*12⌋
            Sim->>Sim: next = clamp(0, capacity, occupied + delta)
            Sim->>DB: UPDATE shopping_centers<br/>SET occupied=next, updated_at=now
            Sim->>Hist: INSERT INTO occupancy_history<br/>(center_id, occupied, capacity, recorded_at)
        end
    end

    Note over FE,Q: A frontend párhuzamosan poll-ozza<br/>a háttér-állapotot

    FE->>Q: useShoppingCenters() (mount/refetch)
    Q->>API: GET /api/shopping-centers
    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM shopping_centers
    DB-->>API: aktualizált foglaltság
    API-->>Q: JSON
    Q-->>FE: cache + re-render<br/>(StatCard, térkép pin színe)
